snippet.title: ELDEN RING - E3 Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
A new world created by Hidetaka Miyazaki and George R.R. Martin

ELDEN RING, developed by FromSoftwareInc., is a fantasy action-RPG adventure set withn a world created by Hidetaka Miyazaki - creator of the influential Dark Souls video game series; and George R.R. Martin - author of the The New York Times best-selling fantasy series, A song of Ice and Fire. Danger and discovery lurk around every corner in FromSoftware's largest game to-date.

Learn more: https://www.xbox.com/games/elden-ring
